<P>
GOLDEN AGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am a golden-ager, and as the term suggests, it will take a ton of gold to 
survive and pay existing insurance premiums. 
</P>
<P>
WINTON R. PUDER 
</P>
<P>
Hacienda Heights 
</P>
