Fortune Petroleum Corp., a small energy concern in Agoura Hills, said it lost 
$27,000 in the first quarter compared with a $47,000 loss a year earlier. 
</P>
<P>
Fortune said the latest loss came despite a 12% increase in revenue, which rose 
to $252,000 in the quarter that ended March 31 from $221,000 a year earlier. 
